<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>BBMS | Home Page</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>

  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="display-5 text-center">Welcome to our Blood Bank Management System (BBMS)</h2>
    <div class="row" style="align-items: center;">
      <img src="images/blood-pint.jpeg" alt="An image of a blood pint"
        class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
      <p class="display-7 col-sm-12 col-md-6" style="font-weight: 300;">
        Welcome to our state-of-the-art Blood Bank System! We are dedicated to saving lives by ensuring a safe and reliable blood supply for those in need. Our advanced platform connects donors, recipients, and healthcare providers, streamlining the process of blood donation and distribution. With our user-friendly interface, you can easily register as a donor, schedule appointments, and track your donations. Together, we can make a difference and contribute to the well-being of our community.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="row" style="align-items: center;">
      <p class="display-7 col-sm-12 col-md-6" style="font-weight: 300;">
        At our Blood Bank System, your contribution matters. Every donation has the power to save lives and make a lasting impact. We prioritize the safety and quality of the blood supply, adhering to the highest standards and implementing rigorous screening processes. Our dedicated team of professionals works diligently to maintain a well-stocked inventory, ensuring that blood is readily available when and where it is needed most. Join us in our mission to provide hope and healing through the gift of life.
      </p>
      <img src="images/hand.jpeg" alt="An image of a blood pint"
        class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
      <p class="display-7 col-sm-12 col-md-12 text-center" style="font-weight: 300;">
        Join our vibrant community of blood donors and recipients, and be a hero in someone's life. Our Blood Bank System offers a range of convenient features that make it easier than ever to get involved. Whether you're a first-time donor or a regular contributor, our platform allows you to manage your donation journey seamlessly. Explore our educational resources, connect with like-minded individuals, and discover the profound impact your generosity can have. Together, we can create a world where no one has to wait for the lifesaving blood they desperately need.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div> 

  <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>